How to use Latex 
use \documentstyle｛carticle｝if we want to use the chinese words.

documentclass【12pt】｛article｝limit the font to 12pt

\newline to make a new line in latex

\newpage to make a new page in latex

\par to make different paragraphs

\（ mathmatic equations\）
$$  mathmatic equations $$

\section*｛xxxx｝
the * says not to number it.If we do not use the * we will get a numbered
section title.

